Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.17,0:02:29.66,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}kono chippoke na ryoute ni nani ga nokotteru darou
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.66,0:02:35.55,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}aoida koe wa sora he chitte itta
