Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.26,0:02:42.43,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}me no mae ga mienaku natte mo
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.72,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}issho nara nagaku tsuzuku kono michi wo
