Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.64,0:02:55.57,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}hokori ni mamireta kizuna mo tsunaideku
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.02,0:03:01.79,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}kako to mirai senaka awase no bokura wa
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.40,0:03:08.96,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}machigai darake no kotae wo kurikaeshite
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.96,0:03:14.21,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}hikari wo motome te wo nobasu yo
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.21,0:03:17.00,OP Romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}nando datte
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.93,0:02:06.43,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}Opakujeme chyby, které nás kdysi zjizvily
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.43,0:02:10.70,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}a hledáme cesty k lepším zítřkům.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.17,0:02:29.66,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\alpha&H50&}Všechno nám propadá našima malýma rukama
